<section id="roadmapSection">
  <h2>Mobile App Development Roadmap</h2>

  <div class="milestone" id="programmingMilestone">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x400/?programming" alt="Programming Icon">
    <h3>Programming Basics</h3>
    <p>Get started with programming. Learn a language like Java, Kotlin (for Android) or Swift (for iOS).</p>
  </div>

  <div class="milestone" id="frameworkMilestone">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x400/?framework" alt="Framework Icon">
    <h3>Mobile App Frameworks</h3>
    <p>Explore popular mobile app frameworks like React Native, Flutter, or Xamarin.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="milestone" id="uiMilestone">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x400/?ui" alt="UI/UX Icon">
    <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>
    <p>Understand the principles of UI/UX design. Create visually appealing and user-friendly interfaces.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="milestone" id="apiMilestone">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x400/?api" alt="API Icon">
    <h3>API Integration</h3>
    <p>Learn how to integrate APIs into your mobile app for fetching data and services.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="milestone" id="databaseMilestone">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x400/?database" alt="Database Icon">
    <h3>Database Management</h3>
    <p>Understand mobile app data storage. Explore databases like SQLite, Firebase, or Realm.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="milestone" id="testingMilestone">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x400/?testing" alt="Testing Icon">
    <h3>Testing and Debugging</h3>
    <p>Learn testing strategies and tools to ensure the reliability of your mobile app.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="milestone" id="deploymentMilestone">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/800x400/?deployment" alt="Deployment Icon">
    <h3>App Deployment</h3>
    <p>Understand the process of deploying mobile apps to app stores. Explore app release and updates.</p>
  </div>
</section>

